<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0f24">
  <title>Solicitud Enviada - MiRestcon IA</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #F0F2F8;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .conf-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px 24px;
      max-width: 380px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(10,15,36,0.08);
    }
    .conf-icon {
      width: 72px;
      height: 72px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef520f, #df2c05);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .conf-title {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0a0f24;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .conf-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #8B8FAD;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .conf-box {
      background: #F0F2F8;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .conf-box p {
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      color: #0a0f24;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .conf-box .step {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .conf-box .step:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .step-dot {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef520f, #df2c05);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }
    .btn-logout {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      background: transparent;
      border: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      color: #8B8FAD;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="conf-card">
    <div class="conf-icon">✓</div>
    <div class="conf-title">¡Solicitud enviada!</div>
    <div class="conf-subtitle">
      Recibimos tu solicitud. Te notificaremos cuando sea aprobada.
    </div>

    <div class="conf-box">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-dot">1</div>
        <p>Revisamos tu información en <strong>24 horas</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-dot">2</div>
        <p>Te notificamos por <strong>email y WhatsApp</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-dot">3</div>
        <p>Accedes a tu sistema para gestionar tu restaurante</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/espera-verificacion" class="btn-logout">Ver estado de mi solicitud</a>
    <a href="/logout" class="btn-logout" style="margin-top:8px;color:#EF4444;border-color:#FEE2E2">Cerrar sesión</a>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/ios-install-banner.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
